Root cause is DOMJSClass.h IsSecureContextOrObjectIsFromSecureContext returns true when Fission on, but expecting false. The test creates an https iframe from an http page, and when fission on, these page content are loaded in different processes. ServiceWorker API uses IsSecureContextOrObjectIsFromSecureContext to check all things are in Secure Context, but it seems not to work in fission environment. Probably all APIs use IsSecureContextOrObjectIsFromSecureContext have the same problem. Bug 1570243 ?
